filteredDispensaries.description:
Your journey with cannabis starts here.

At Due North Cannabis, we go above and beyond to create unique and inviting spaces that speak to our Northern heritage . Our goal is to empower our customers to discover new and exciting cannabis products and accessories. Come and visit our locally owned Cannabis Cabins for a retail experience unlike any other.

FREE DELIVERY ON ORDERS OVER $20!!! 🚚💨

90 MINUTE DELIVERY WINDOW!⏰🍃


Delivery orders under $20 are subject to $4.20 fee. Deliveries must be paid for in advance. Orders leave the store between 11am and 7pm

Orders placed before 11am will leave the store at 11am. Orders placed after 7pm will be delivered the following day. Please have your ID and credit card ready for delivery orders. Apartment building tenants must meet our drivers in the lobby.


We accept credit, debit, cash and e-transfers!


HOME OF THE DAILY SPECIAL!🎉😲

Munchie Monday 🍬 - Save 15% on Edibles

510 Tuesday - Save 13% on Vape Cartridges and PAX Pods!

Wellness Wednesday 💚 - Save 15% on Topicals, Oils, Capsules and a selection of CBD, CBN and CBG products 

Thirsty Thursday 🍹 - Save 15% on Beverages

Feature Friday 🔥 - Save 13% on Featured Brands

*NEW* Shatter Saturday ✨- Save 15% on concentrates!

Sativa Sunday 🌟 - Select Sativa Flower & Pre Rolls 15% off!


No "stacking" of multiple discounts. Loyalty points are earned by visiting our stores, no purchase necessary. Some loyalty discounts are in store only.
